Myles Standish State Park Road Race
HWC Time Trial Series
description: 8 Race T.T. series on two different course.Races are held on the first and third Tuesday of the month.Point will be awarded per race using a handicap system based on age and gender.Series winners will be determined from the best ive race point totals.
course: 1st Tuesday course:5.7 mile-1000ft. vertical starting in S. Egremont and finishing at the Mt. Everett parking area.3rd Tuesday course:10 milee rolling hill loop in Alford. Start and finish in Alford Ctr.
registration: Registration opens at 5:15.First rider starts at 6:00P.USCF license required and must be presented at registration.One day licenses will be available.On-line registration at www.bikereg.com.Entry fee $5 per race.$10 for 8/21/07 race in Alford.HWC members race free except 8/21/07 race-Fee $10.
notes: Roads open to traffic during race.Please use caution when overtaking slower racers.
directions: First Tuesday(S.Egremont)From South:Take Route 7N to left on Route 41/23.Take left on Route 41S and right to Mt.Washington Rd.Left at intersection.Parking on right.From North:Take Route 7S to right on 41/23 follow above directions to course.Second Tuesday course(Alford): Take Route7N(If coming from the South)and Route7N (If coming from the North)Take left (From S)or right (from N)on to Maple Ave.Follow to Alford Ctr.Park at cemetery on right.
